{"tid":2041266,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"律師會改選五理事  民主派「8964」奪四席","createTime":"2020-05-29T06:30:45.000Z","updateTime":"2020-05-29T09:11:21.000Z","uid":25558,"like":16,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":6,"replies":[{"pid":"18bc669c7644a9005e11c7700061907bb4d8c46e","tid":2041266,"uid":25558,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-29T06:30:45.000Z","msg":"全文<br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.news.appledaily.com/local/20200529/YGBGHOQJHSIFMDRXVNYRI44NQM/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20200529%2FYGBGHOQJHSIFMDRXVNYRI44NQM%2F&d=nsl8wma01YyMGEZOa9B33Fuzyl20%2B4TZ9N3SWLiWM4Y%3D&h=b44a9d2e\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20200529%2FYGBGHOQJHSIFMDRXVNYRI44NQM%2F&h=1155bf66\" target=\"_blank\">https://hk.news.appledaily.com/local/20200529/YGBGHOQJHSIFMDRXVNYRI44NQM/</a><br />\n<br />\n律師會改選五理事 <br />\n民主派「8964」奪四席<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://cloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com/appledaily/UAS6NX26JCON3RGXIMHBRPLDYY.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com%2Fappledaily%2FUAS6NX26JCON3RGXIMHBRPLDYY.jpg&h=2aa9d5b0&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n左起：彭皓昕、林洋鋐、蔡頴德、黃耀初當選後見傳媒。林俊謙攝<br />\n<br />\n【本報訊】香港律師會昨晚舉行周年大會，同時改選理事會其中五個席位，有表明力爭成立獨立調查委員會的義務律師團隊及包括人權律師林洋鋐在內的民主派隊伍，經協調下全力爭取入局。受近一年社會運動影響，昨親自出席選舉的會員人數眾多，令點票延至凌晨才有結果，最終民主派成功取下四席，料可令理事會內民主派聲音倍增。<br />\n<br />\n律師會共20名理事，今屆需改選當中五個席位，據悉包括熊運信、羅睿德、莊偉倫、黃吳潔華及馬華潤，改選共有10人角逐，其中羅睿德及莊偉倫爭取連任，另有五人名單被視為民主開明派，當中包括前年曾參選但落敗的律師林洋鋐，今年聯同另外兩名在反修例運動中任義。。。。。。。。。。。委員會委員黃耀初合組另一名單參選，望改該會保守作風。蔡梓蘊及後宣佈為大局決定棄選。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n林洋鋐取3,198票成票王<br />\n<br />\n改選投票昨晚8時50分截止，經近四小時點票後，今日凌晨近1時才公佈結果，被視為民主派代表的林洋鋐、彭皓昕、蔡頴德及黃耀初當選，林洋鋐更獲3,198票成「票王」；而四人候選號碼分別為4、6、8及9，能湊成敏感的「8964」組合，餘下一席由莊偉倫連任。雖然民主派大比。。。。。。。。。。。。帝理邁被視為民主派，料難即時對律師會產生影響，亦不足以影響會長選舉，但確令理事會內民主派聲音倍增。<br />\n<br />\n周年大會上不少律師質疑現任會長彭韻僖早前大量發電郵，籲會員支持五名。。。。。。。。。。。選舉，亦有會員要求彭考慮不要運用自己的授權票，但終被拒絕。"},{"pid":"47f700ffe6427b5cb2358b8092c7151b8303b1f6","tid":2041266,"uid":155784,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-29T07:27:07.000Z","msg":"蔡律師好靚女<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/wet.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/wet.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/wet.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f0e1b6c8fd491f1f5d9fd6b421c4b480c7bdcb37","tid":2041266,"uid":286792,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-29T07:34:13.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"944406e8e07e03d58f19b0c8e66057b2f7f9f2a3","tid":2041266,"uid":49329,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-29T07:40:05.000Z","msg":"8964 天意！"},{"pid":"ec24a05fcd1dcb393ed8f955892c1f8794e9c9e1","tid":2041266,"uid":3149,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-29T07:55:52.000Z","msg":"Push <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0551c6ef4ca37430ed6d9f06a926439cb3d39bb3","tid":2041266,"uid":27008,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-05-29T08:08:29.000Z","msg":"依加理事20個入面得依4個係開明  其他全藍?"},{"pid":"ea1ecdd80d0ef0152961cc50bb80a30b575d39ea","tid":2041266,"uid":25558,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"0551c6ef4ca37430ed6d9f06a926439cb3d39bb3","tid":2041266,"uid":27008,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-05-29T08:08:29.000Z","msg":"依加理事20個入面得依4個係開明  其他全藍?"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-29T09:11:21.000Z","msg":"重有<br />\n張達明 同「人權律師」帝理邁"}]}